<Word Search Puzzles> by Dave Shin

<DESCRIPTION>
An interactive and customizable word search puzzle generator made with Unity/C#. 
Simply insert any word you want inside the wordpool.txt, and configure the settings via the "Word Search" script attached to the "Main Camera" in Unity Inspector.

